Localization.Name: Roberts Space Industries
Localization.Description: The original creators of the engine that kickstarted Humanity’s expansion into space, Roberts Space Industries builds a wide range of spaceships that serve all needs, from basic interstellar travel to deep exploration on the outer edges of the galaxy. The tagline is “Roberts Space Industries: Delivering the Stars since 2075”

Localization.Name: Venture Undersuit Alpha
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Undersuit
Damage Reduction: 10%
Temp. Rating: -30 / 60 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 8.0 µSCU

Whether you’re discovering bold new frontiers or simply stretching your legs after a long spaceflight, Robert Space Industries’ Venture Explorer Suit takes vacuum-safe wear to the next level with its incorporation of top-of-class safety features seamlessly blended with phenomenal freedom of movement.
